title: The Habits to Build Your Life
itunes:title: The Habits to Build Your Life
description:
Episode 450 - 47% of what we do every day is habits. We are on autopilot during those times. We need to take a step back and assess if those habits are the ones that we want controlling our lives. In this episode, I break down how to create the habits that you want and destroy the ones that you do not.
